name: Dynamic Gallery Fixed
description:
very minute this OBJKT selects one of it's owners chosen at random and displays their creations in the picture frame. If the current user shown doesn't have any creations their collection is shown instead.

** This is a very early implementation of this technology and will break if the API's it uses change. Subject to bugs and API request limitations, so be patient :]

** if you bought the previous version this one is fixed
